      "text": "How YouTube’s Elections Policies Work Given the global nature of our platform, our elections policies and systems are developed and implemented with a global view - our Community Guidelines are enforced across languages and locales, and our systems connect voters across all of the countries we operate in to high-quality news and information about the elections that are most relevant to them.",
